'''Lawrence Vidya Bhawan''' is a co-educational school located at [[Rajbagh]] in [[Srinagar]], [[Jammu & Kashmir]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ekikrat.in/schools-srinagar|title=Schools in Srinagar {{!}} Ekikrat.in|website=ekikrat.in|language=en|access-date=2017-12-26}}</ref>

==History==
LVB is part of the Lawrence Group of Schools. The branch at [[Rajbagh]] was opened in the year 1995. During 2014, the second branch was opened in [[Soura]].

==Education==
The [[school]] has four departments that provide co-ed classes from [[Nursery school|Nursery]] to 10th.  
